58
00:04:02,953 --> 00:04:05,387
I've got a meeting and so do you...

59
00:04:05,633 --> 00:04:07,510
...you elitist Harvard fascist...

60
00:04:07,713 --> 00:04:11,183
...missed-the-Dean's-List-
two-semesters-in-a-row...

61
00:04:11,433 --> 00:04:13,503
